{"type": "article", "id": 13835, "title": "充电手环", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-21T08:09:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 59, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606140507S1giVsKAdhxU2TJG.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tAdapt Technology 最近推出了一款充电手环，他其实是一根连接线，兼容手机，相机和 Micro USB 各类设备，不使用时可以变成手环携带，因为它在设计上也十分时尚，硅树脂的材质，黑色，白色和灰色三款配色，看上去不错。产品售价 25 美元，将于这个周末登陆 Adapt Technology 官方网站，<a href=\"http://adapt.technology/pages/shop\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以购买。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141515C8wYrZKDlMneRcjA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141516J5j0MsvxXVQtnaOP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141516AdY2S8RpgJi9L0Kv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141517MuP3lwQn1LJHeF2C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141517GkKfjrmodqJzZVOD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<br>\n\n\n\n"}